Text.Value: Perform Back Light Test
• Press and release the LIGHT button
• The back light will turn on for approximately 5 seconds
• If necessary, cup your hand around the LCD screen to observe the back light

If at any time a blinking lower-case "b" appears on the LCD, the batteries have been discharged beyond the level where the unit can operate. Replace the batteries immediately to continue any type of operation on the UDR-14 Radiac.
PRE-OPERATIONAL TEST PROCEDURE
